{"id":239801,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/维权网-湖南岳阳政府掩埋房屋和鱼池逼养殖户签/","date":"2012-07-13T20:45:58Z","modified":"2012-07-13T20:45:58Z","title":"维权网 | 湖南岳阳政府掩埋房屋和鱼池逼养殖户签协议（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span> </span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><br /><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员方芳报道）湖南省岳阳市的政绩工程“临港产业新区”的建设，需要征收云溪区养殖户李元科、李群科、陈新贵的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">40</span><span>多亩养殖场和养鱼池，为了逼迫他们签订不合理的征收协议，当地政府雇佣</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>多名经过培训的年轻人做“保安”和打手，出动多辆工程车运送建筑垃圾和土石方，来掩埋</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>名养殖户的房屋和鱼池。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据李元科、李群科、陈新贵反映：他们</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>人是当地的专业养殖户，每家年均出栏生猪</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">500</span><span>多头，水产品（多种淡水鱼及甲鱼等）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>万多斤，每年的经济效益相当可观，这几年都过上了小康生活。但岳阳“临港产业新区”的建设，使他们面临灭顶之灾。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>当地政府官员曾多次对他们说：“你们修建的精养渔池等级太高，政府如果按照法律规定的补偿标准补偿，根本赔偿不起，所以你们根本不可能获得补偿。”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span><span>　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日</span><span>，为了逼迫李元科、李群科、陈新贵</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>名养殖户签订不合理的补偿协议，当地政府没有履行任何法律手续，雇佣</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>多名经过培训的年轻人做“保安”和打手，乡政府主要负责人现场亲自指挥</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>出动多辆工程车</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>小时不停的运送建筑垃圾和土石方，来掩埋</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>名养殖户的房屋和鱼池。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>李元科、李群科、陈新贵花费巨资修建的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">40</span><span>多亩精养鱼池被夷为平地，养殖池里的鱼和甲鱼被掩埋在土石方下，房屋被土石方掩埋的只露出一个屋顶，面对虎视眈眈的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>多名打手，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>名养殖户只能眼睁睁的看着自己的血汗被毁于一旦。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-bE0HjXMeAu8/UABMaF4f3yI/AAAAAAAAJQA/QD-dHXeiIg8/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"217\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-bE0HjXMeAu8/UABMaF4f3yI/AAAAAAAAJQA/QD-dHXeiIg8/s320/1.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span>工程车在用拉来的建筑垃圾和土方掩埋房屋和鱼池</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-XJywwWPOjVc/UABMdj2RwuI/AAAAAAAAJQI/0IDUgdc0xws/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"215\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-XJywwWPOjVc/UABMdj2RwuI/AAAAAAAAJQI/0IDUgdc0xws/s320/2.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span>鱼池中的鱼被掩埋的土呛得蹦出水面被捡起</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-vzzXJR51HPk/UABMhTxNM_I/AAAAAAAAJQQ/_UE8cJLk-hY/s1600/3.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"216\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-vzzXJR51HPk/UABMhTxNM_I/AAAAAAAAJQQ/_UE8cJLk-hY/s320/3.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span>被掩埋后死去的甲鱼</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-x3cPey3CXv4/UABMkrQAVtI/AAAAAAAAJQY/fOMEeNwtL3c/s1600/4.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"214\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-x3cPey3CXv4/UABMkrQAVtI/AAAAAAAAJQY/fOMEeNwtL3c/s320/4.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span>被掩埋的只露出屋顶的房子</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-SuPmo_W_524/UABMnHVTJPI/AAAAAAAAJQg/RuNyO4941bk/s1600/5.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"215\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-SuPmo_W_524/UABMnHVTJPI/AAAAAAAAJQg/RuNyO4941bk/s320/5.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span>政府雇佣的部分打手</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<p><span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-8042111298998542353?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/12355e2f1.jpg-150x150.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}